The Adirondack Trust Company - Saratoga Springs Bank & Local Bank. Banking. Insurance. Investments. 
As a leading bank in the community, The Adirondack Trust Company takes great pride in providing individuals and businesses in the Saratoga and Warren County Region with high quality banking, trust and investment and insurance solutions. With the convenience of twelve local branches and access to your accounts through our online banking services, banking has never been easier.
Our services are customized to help you reach your financial goals, whether it's a savings account designed to pay for college or a small business loan to help your company grow. As you analyze your financial needs, please review the services we provide so we can help you build your comprehensive financial strategy:

Personal Banking
Savings Accounts
Online Banking
Checking Accounts
Home Mortgages
Personal Loans
Insurance
Trust and Investments, including individualized retirement planning
Business Banking, including checking and savings accounts along with commercial mortgages


Please contact us with any questions about our services. We always appreciate hearing from our customers and visitors.

 
  Investment & Insurance Products are: NOT A DEPOSIT * NOT FDIC INSURED * NOT GUARANTEED BY THE BANK * NOT INSURED BY    ANY GOVERNMENT AGENCY * MAY GO DOWN IN VALUE 




  






 
 

 

 
  









 

 


 
 
 
 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
